text_show:
Mwatoñojokaña nenu yuma yinakumwekana mukaayi . . . yikatwalekahu chochenichi? yikataminaku? yikawahilaku? BAYIBOLU YAHOSHAÑA NAWU “Nzambi . . . wakayikombola madilu ejima kumesu awu; hikwakekala nawa cheñi kufwaku; hikwakekala nawa cheñi hela kuneña hela kudila hela kukataku. Yuma yakusambila yinahiti dehi.”—Chimwekeshu 21:3, 4. ICHI CHIKANINU CHIKAHIMPA CHIHANDILU CHENU Mwakazataña nyidimu yayiwahi yakudiluñisha.—Isaya 65:21-23. Hikwakekala yikatu hela yihuñuku.—Isaya 25:8; 33:24. Mwakashakama
..........
) Dikwila nawu wudi nawuswa chikupu wakwila mwakanayi kulonda yabalumuni dinu ituña nakudiwahisha chiwahi. Kwesekeja nachahosha Bayibolu, “yuma yejima yinatwesheki kudi Nzambi.”—Matewu 19:26. Nzambi nakufwila kwila mwakanayi. Chakutalilahu, Yehova ‘nakufwila’ kusha cheñi muuya mudi antu afwa dehi.—Yoba 14:14, 15. Bayibolu yatulejaña cheñi nawu Mwana kaNzambi, Yesu, wokileña akata. Muloñadi? Muloña dichakeñeleñayi. (Maku 1:40, 41) Yesu wembujolileña chiwahi yililu yaTata yindi kuhitila mukufwila
